<D>__{i know you think look at me. hey. edith.}
<C>__{richie dimaso }
<D>__{i know you think irv loves you. i know you think you know him that he sees the world as a cold, dark place, and he cares about nobody but very few people on his short list: his son, his father, rosalyn, and you. and you think you're at the top of that list. but what if you're not. what if you're not even on the list at all? he'd be in here right now if he took the check.}
