<C>__{richie dimaso }
<D>__{he'd be in here right now if he took the check. but no, you did. god, it's, it's so clear to me. it's so crazy it's clear to me, but it's not clear to you. he uses you, edith, to protect himself. to protect his son and his wife in long island. no? yes. he put a ring on her finger, he adopted her son. they have huge house, they have two cars. what does she do all day? i will tell you what she does she plays with her nails, she watches t.v., and she spends your money, the money that you make.}
